#  Single Ta atom in a big box (BCC), treated with spin-orbit coupling.

 acell 3*12.00
 ecut 5
 enunit 2
 kptopt 0
 nkpt  1
 intxc 1
 istwfk 1
 kpt  0.0 0.0 0.0
 ixc 2
 natom  1 nband 18
 nspinor 2
 nline 5  nstep 10
 ntypat  1
 occopt  7
 rprim   0.5 .5 -.5 -.5 0.5 .5 .5 -.5 0.5
 toldfe 1.0d-7
 tsmear 0.01
 typat  1
 xred  0.0 0.0 0.0
 znucl 73.0


